    "4013905": {
        "Desc": "Go to the docks",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Gaming walks forward and exchanges a few words with a boatman near the docks. The next thing you know, he's called for everyone to board a bamboo raft..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Finally, we can rest! Paimon's shoulders are so stiff, and her stomach's so empty..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "Sorry, sorry! Did I push the pace a bit too much? I mean, you were the ones who said you were travel experts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Liyue's just too hilly. Floating up and down so much wears Paimon out. *sigh* Paimon was finally satisfied, and now her poor stomach's empty again..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "Would you like some Winter Melon Cake? I have some on me that I bought from a store."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yes! Paimon'll take all you've got!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "You might want to pace yourself there or you'll be too full to eat a proper meal later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Pfft, Paimon never gets too full! Just like... Oh! Just like you, apparently, never get tired, no matter how far you walk or how many jobs you work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "#Ah, I see. Then here you go, Paimon. And for you, {NICKNAME}. Enjoy!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "And here's some for you too, Uncle Bosu. Don't think I forgot about you, my friend. I'll just set it to the side here for ya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Gaming seems like a real people person. He can get along with anyone, and he treats every person he meets like a close friend.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ah, that hit the spot! Paimon thought she was going to starve to death for a minute there!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "Ha, that close of a call, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "I've been eating Winter Melon Cake ever since I was a kid. You can buy them from all sorts of places, whether it's a small vendor on the side of the road or a big restaurant in the city, but each place produces cakes with a slightly different flavor."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "If you like these ones, I can give you the address of the shop I bought them from. I'll just have to check when we get back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "Ah! All my jabbering must be making it difficult for you to enjoy the scenery in peace. Don't be afraid to tell me to zip it for a little while, okay? Really, I won't be offended."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's okay! Paimon is kind of enjoying listening to your chitter-chatter."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Gaming",
                    "T": "Aw, a fed Paimon is a happy Paimon, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Paimon can be in a good mood any time she wants!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
